high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the orange cup that is in the sink.
With the cup in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave door.  Place the cup in the microwave and shut the door.  Start the microwave.  When done take the cup out and shut the door.
With the cup in hand move over so you can reach the cabinet above the microwave that is on the left.
Open the cupboard that is on the left above the microwave.  Place the cup in front of the lotion that is on the second shelf.  Shut the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Warm a cup up and put it away in cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the sink.
Take the cup from the sink.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the oven. Go forward to the oven.
Put the cup in the microwave above the oven to heat it. Take the cup from the microwave.
Look up at the left cabinet above the microwave.
Put the cup in the left cabinet above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and find the sink.
Pick up the glass from in the sink.
Hold the glass and turn around, then find the microwave on the right.
Open the microwave and place the glass inside. Then shut the door, and open it again and take out the glass. Shut the door.
Hold the glass and look down, then up again.
Open the top left cabinet and place the glass inside.
anns.task_desc: Heat a glass and put it in a cabinet.
